== N'abrabɔmu Nsɛm ==
Ɔware  Mr. Kojo Safo akyire a ɔhyia no wɔ mmerɛ ana ɔkɔ sukuu wɔ University of Ghana na ɔtoa ne kunu no so wɔ Alataman mu wɔ afe 1982; ɛhɔ na ɔhyɛ ase sɛ ɔrekyerɛ brofo kasa no ase ɛwɔ Methodist Comprehensive High School a ewɔ Ekiti State. Ɔmo san nso ba ɔman Ghana mu  afe mmiɛnsa.<ref name="Bruinhorst">{{Cite web}}</ref>

== Owuo ne Ayieyɔ ==
Safo ɛwu wɔ 37 Military Hospital ɛda a ɛtoso Kotonimma 8, 2014. Wɔn ɛdeda no wɔ Osu Cemetery ɛda Memeneda, Ayɛwohomumɔ 28. Ɔde n'akyi ɛgya ne kunu ne ne mma  ɛnan.<ref name="Bruinhorst">{{Cite web}}</ref><ref name="Bruinhorst"/>

